<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 13:06:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189</link><description>&lt;p&gt;又一周了！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 19:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-189</guid></item><item><title>美国正在努力防止伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡埋设地雷</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-efforts-to-prevent-iranian-mine-laying-in-strait-of-hormuz-underway</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着第三支航母打击群抵达该地区，另一个美国代表团正前往巴基斯坦，试图重启谈判。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-efforts-to-prevent-iranian-mine-laying-in-strait-of-hormuz-underway"&gt;美国努力防止伊朗在霍尔木兹海峡埋设地雷的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 19:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-efforts-to-prevent-iranian-mine-laying-in-strait-of-hormuz-underway</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰的无人机狩猎 An-28 涡轮螺旋桨飞机现在正在发射拦截无人机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-drone-hunting-an-28-turboprop-is-now-launching-interceptor-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰坚固耐用的 An-28 Cash 涡轮螺旋桨反无人机平台的最新发展结合了拦截无人机和转轮机枪武器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-drone-hunting-an-28-turboprop-is-now-launching-interceptor-drones"&gt;乌克兰狩猎无人机的 An-28 涡轮螺旋桨飞机正在发射拦截无人机，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 18:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-drone-hunting-an-28-turboprop-is-now-launching-interceptor-drones</guid></item><item><title>HH-60W 战斗救援直升机将在首都承担末日疏散任务</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/hh-60w-combat-rescue-helicopters-to-take-on-doomsday-evacuation-role-in-the-nations-capital</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Jolly Green II 将进行改装，用于 VIP 空运和政府行动的连续性，取代老化的 UH-1N 双休伊飞机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/hh-60w-combat-rescue-helicopters-to-take-on-doomsday-evacuation-role-in-the-nations-capital"&gt;HH-60W 后战斗救援直升机将在国家首都承担末日疏散任务，该&lt;/a&gt;直升机首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 16:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/hh-60w-combat-rescue-helicopters-to-take-on-doomsday-evacuation-role-in-the-nations-capital</guid></item><item><title>Saildrone 携带导弹的 Spectre 参加海军中型无人船竞赛</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Saildrone 与国防巨头联手，扩大其经过验证的车辆概念，并为其配备导弹和潜艇搜索传感器。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition"&gt;Saildrone 携带导弹的“幽灵”号参加海军中型无人舰艇竞赛的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 23:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/saildrones-missile-toting-spectre-enters-navys-medium-sized-unmanned-ship-competition</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对伊朗小船下达杀戮令（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普还表示，他将把海峡的排雷工作增加“三倍”，尽管目前还不清楚这些活动目前正在进行什么（如果有的话）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats"&gt;特朗普对伊朗小船下达杀戮令（更新）的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 22:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/trump-puts-out-kill-order-on-irans-small-boats</guid></item><item><title>NASA 777 飞行实验室降落在兰利</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley</link><description>&lt;p&gt;NASA 最大的研究飞机将接替该机构标志性的 DC-8，并计划于 2027 年进行首次测试。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley"&gt;NASA 777 飞行实验室降落在兰利的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 20:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/nasas-777-flying-laboratory-touches-down-at-langley</guid></item><item><title>海军急忙用地狱火导弹武装航母战斗群</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着单向攻击无人机日益增长的威胁，海军正在为其舰队提供更多的反无人机硬杀伤能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy"&gt;海军用地狱火导弹冲向航母战斗群&lt;/a&gt;后，首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 18:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/rush-to-arm-carrier-strike-groups-with-hellfire-missiles-for-anti-drone-defense-disclosed-by-navy</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击改变了海军在中东加油的方式</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国海军创建了一种商业“油轮跑步机”，用于在海上给油轮加油，提供的经验教训可能会对未来的行动产生更大的影响。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east"&gt;伊朗袭击后改变了海军在中东加油的方式&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/iranian-attacks-change-way-navy-refuels-its-ships-in-middle-east</guid></item><item><title>特朗普停火延期后，伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</link><description>&lt;p&gt;由于伊朗拒绝承诺进行和谈，停火的未来仍然存在疑问。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension"&gt;特朗普停火延期后伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</guid></item></channel></rss>